gdome2
------------------------------------------
DOM C library developped for the Gnome project

Runtime requirements:
  bash-5.2.21-1
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libgdome-devel-0.8.1-1bl3
  libgdome0-0.8.1-1bl3
  libglib2.0-devel-2.88.1-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.88.1-1
  libxml2-2.10.4-2
  libxml2-devel-2.10.4-2
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  libglib2.0-devel-2.88.1-1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  libxml2-devel-2.10.4-2
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  http://gdome2.cs.unibo.it/

Canonical download:
  http://gdome2.cs.unibo.it/tarball/gdome2-0.8.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack gdome2-0.8.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./gdome2-0.8.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/gdome2-0.8.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/gdome2-0.8.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgdome0-0.8.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgdome-devel-0.8.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

